WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.175
In Campaigns you plan marketing by segment.

00:00:03.175 --> 00:00:07.828
In Email you build templates, send, and track opens and clicks.

00:00:07.828 --> 00:00:10.855
And you can automate sequences by trigger

00:00:10.855 --> 00:00:14.400
for example, as soon as a new client is created.
